Login Page

In this exercise lab, you would have to try and replicate the codedamn's login page design.

The main compoenents of this login page design are
Heading (already built for you)
Input Fields & Forgot Password
Sign up Button
OAuth Buttons
Recaptcha Privacy Policy Text

Challenges:
Create a HTML Form element
Create Inputs & Labels for the username and password fields & style them with proper width, border radius etc.
Create a flex element for Remember me and forgot password text
Create a spacer for text "or continue with"
Create buttons for OAuth elements and add SVG's from the assets folder
Add a recaptcha privacy policy text at the bottom of the form
